Canonical website:
  https://github.com/airsim/tvlsim

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/airsim/tvlsim/archive/refs/tags/v1.01.11.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack tvlsim-1.01.11-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./tvlsim-1.01.11-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/tvlsim-1.01.11-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/tvlsim-1.01.11-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libtvlsim1.01-1.01.11-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libtvlsim-devel-1.01.11-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

